Yeah, it's just a public affairs team.

187
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:11,500
回头我向你报告  你明天再打给他们
I'll brief you, and then you can call them tomorrow.

188
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:12,820
你去接孩子吧
Go get your kids.

189
00:08:33,530 --> 00:08:36,200
雷米今天早上去过我办公室
Remy came by this morning. To the office.

190
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:37,600
