- You said no, right? - I didn't.

194
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:47,960
他并不图你任何回报  弗兰西斯
He doesn't want anything from you, Francis.

195
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,920
得了吧  克莱尔  你这还不懂吗
Come on, Claire. You know better than that.

196
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,740
我特意问过的
I specifically asked.

197
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,310
