Maybe not right now,

198
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:55,740
他是我一手提拔的
but look, I invented this guy, all right?

199
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:56,990
迈出这一步就刹不住了
It's a slippery slope. You...

200
00:08:56,990 --> 00:08:58,200
想想有了这笔钱我能做多少事
Think of what I can do with this money.

201
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,690
