I can hire back the people I let go.

202
00:09:00,690 --> 00:09:02,940
还能加快吉莉安那些项目的
I can help accelerate the funding for the projects

203
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,180
融资进度
that Gillian has brought in.

204
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:05,690
资金的事我们可以另想办法
Let's find another way to raise the money.

205
00:09:05,690 --> 00:09:07,480
但这笔钱唾手可得
But it's right there at my feet.

206
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,920
克莱尔  我现在已经百事缠身了
Claire, I have too much on my plate right now.

207
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,220
不能再被桑科公司纠缠上
I can't have San corp breathing down my neck again.

208
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:13,520
我不能让雷米
I can't have Remy...

209
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,290
那是雷米啊
Look, it is Remy.

210
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:17,650
他太了解我了  这很危险
He knows me too well. It's dangerous.

211
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:19,930
要顾全大局
Look at the bigger picture here.

212
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:24,170
我恳求你
I'm asking.

213
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:25,900
你这不是恳求
No. You're not.

214
00:09:31,650 --> 00:09:32,900
克莱尔
Claire.

215
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,810
