- How much? - 200,000.

302
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,270
一个项目就要这么多
For one project?

303
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:07,350
我知道很多
I know it's a lot,

304
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,750
但这是我们在非洲的旗舰项目
but it'll be our flagship project in Africa,

305
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:12,090
我们也是那里首家
and we would be the first organization there

306
00:13:12,090 --> 00:13:13,730
有如此规模的机构
to work on this scale.

307
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,910
