I'd like to go over the specifics first.

308
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:17,090
我已经做好了预算表
I have the budget right here.

309
00:13:17,090 --> 00:13:18,870
我先查一下留言  就去找你
Let me just grab my messages, and then I'll come in to you.

310
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,590
好  我在办公室等你
Okay. I'll be in my office.

311
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:23,720
