Any calls while I was out?

312
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:26,580
都放你桌上了  这个是快递送来的
They're on the desk, and this came by messenger.

313
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:46,450
克莱尔  你不需要桑科  你有我呢  弗兰克

314
00:14:06,690 --> 00:14:08,350
亚当  我是克莱尔
Adam. It's Claire.

315
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,840
对  我知道  是这样
Yes. I know. It has.

316
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:18,250
没事  只是想你了
No reason. I was just thinking about you.

317
00:14:21,090 --> 00:14:22,890
你说得对  是谎话
You're right. It is a lie.

318
00:14:23,050 --> 00:14:24,450
我确实有事
I do have a reason.

319
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:27,040
我需要你
I need to use you.

320
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:29,190
白宫就是新闻死掉的地方
The White House is where news goes to die.

321
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:30,310
净是些陈词滥调
Everything's canned.

322
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:32,320
那些精心编排的讲话...
These perfectly prepared statements...

323
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,580
那是份威风的工作  佐伊
it's a prestigious job, Zoe.

324
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:35,840
