Used to be, when I was in ninth grade.

325
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,440
现在就是块墓地
Now it's a graveyard.

326
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,480
现在唯一还算有意思的事
The only halfway interesting thing they do

327
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:41,540
