is throw a big dinner party once a year

328
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,180
他们不是自我吹捧
where they pat themselves on the back

329
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:45,050
就是跟明星勾肩搭背
and rub shoulders with movie stars.

330
00:14:45,050 --> 00:14:46,130
谁要看那个
Who needs that?

331
00:14:46,130 --> 00:14:47,290
从你到这里开始
Every day since you started here,

332
00:14:47,290 --> 00:14:49,160
每天都在求我给你升职  而现在...
you've begged me to move you up, and now...

333
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,550
我的人生理想
My goal in life is not

334
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,800
不是在《先驱报》一步步爬到
to climb up the Herald's ladder one rung at a time

335
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:54,670
我能有自己的文具
until I've got my own stationery.

336
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:57,210
我们有些人很珍惜在这样一家报社的发展
Some of us value a career at a paper like this.

337
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,870
抱歉  我不是那个意思...
I'm sorry. I didn't mean for that to come off...

338
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:02,340
