one person who can deliver 12.

355
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,280
黑人党团
The black caucus.

356
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,390
乌麦克
Womack.

357
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:46,990
我们给他什么好处
What can we offer him?

358
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:47,980
他需要什么
What does he need?

359
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,490
