395
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:26,340
安德伍德议员是爸爸的老板
Congressman Underwood is daddy's boss.

396
00:17:26,340 --> 00:17:28,100
我还以为你没有老板
I thought you didn't have a boss.

397
00:17:29,340 --> 00:17:30,560
人人都有老板  甜心
Everybody has a boss, sweetheart,

398
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:31,410
议员也不例外
even congressmen.

399
00:17:31,410 --> 00:17:33,190
把晚餐拿去卧室里吃吧
Why don't you take your dinner and go into the bedroom?

400
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:35,490
-可我想看电视  -现在就去
- But I wanted to watch TV. - Go now.

401
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:37,270
孩子们很可爱
Cute kids.

402
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:38,620
是啊  我爱他们
Yeah, I like them.

403
00:17:38,970 --> 00:17:39,950
来杯喝的怎么样
Can I get you a drink?

404
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:41,660
不用  我很快就走
No, I won't be here long.

405
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:43,670
好的  请坐
Yeah. Have a seat.

406
00:17:43,910 --> 00:17:45,330
谢谢
Oh, thanks.

407
00:17:45,740 --> 00:17:47,560
那是索尼次时代掌机吗
Is that a ps vita?

408
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,680
都有什么游戏
Which games does he have?

409
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:53,790
一应俱全
All of them.

410
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:54,930
我家有个游戏机
I have a console at home.

411
00:17:54,930 --> 00:17:56,720
我常用来放松
I play sometimes to relax.

412
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,700
我该买台这个放车上
I ought to get one of these for the car.

413
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,470
彼得
So, Peter,

414
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:06,020
