we need to close the shipyard in your district.

415
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:07,340
明天军事基地整合委员会听证会
The BRAC hearing is tomorrow.

416
00:18:07,340 --> 00:18:08,820
你不要努力争取
You won't put up your usual fight.

417
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:11,240
