rather than look it in the mouth.

503
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,370
这张很不错
That's nice.

504
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:22,330
我是在阿姆拉维蒂外的一个小镇上看到她的
I found her in a village outside Amravati.

505
00:22:22,330 --> 00:22:24,030
她叫蒂阿拉
Her name was Tiala.

506
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:26,420
