She died three weeks after I took that picture.

507
00:22:26,420 --> 00:22:27,920
这太可怕了
Oh, that's awful.

508
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:30,100
如果你喜欢  就都给你
You can have them all if you like.

509
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,420
我喜欢你短发的样子
I love your hair short.

510
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:38,650
今晚有安排吗
Do you have plans tonight?

511
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:42,080
没有
No.

512
00:22:42,080 --> 00:22:44,340
弗兰克会在家等你吗
Is Frank expecting you home?

513
00:22:44,340 --> 00:22:46,220
我想他应该会很晚到家
I'm sure he'll be home late.

514
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:48,230
和我一起吃晚餐
Get dinner with me.

515
00:22:49,820 --> 00:22:51,380
你几点的火车
What time is your train?

516
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:53,710
我没订返程票
I don't book round-trip tickets.

517
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:58,730
我还要好一会儿才能下班
It's going to be a while before I can leave.

518
00:22:58,730 --> 00:23:00,130
几点结束
What time will you be done?

519
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:04,530
大概八点左右
Probably around 8:00.

520
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,180
我去选个地方
I'll pick a place,

521
00:23:07,970 --> 00:23:09,160
选好之后跟你说
let you know.

522
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,780
大卫
Ah. David.

523
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:25,860
还好吗  乔
How are you, Joe?

524
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:29,370
我站在你这边  我们好好干
I'm behind you. Let's do this.

525
00:23:29,370 --> 00:23:30,600
干什么
Do what?

526
00:23:31,470 --> 00:23:33,180
保持谨慎
Keep your cards close.

527
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,760
我喜欢
I like that.

528
