Actually, could you make that two bottles?

532
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:32,390
谢谢
Thank you.

533
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:35,450
坐吧  你这样我紧张
Sit down. You're making me nervous.

534
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:44,880
-你还抽烟吗  -偶尔还抽
- You still smoke? - From time to time, yes.

535
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:50,950
我戒了  这些都是幻觉
I quit. These are an illusion.

536
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:53,170
来一根
You want?

537
00:24:53,630 --> 00:24:54,900
好啊
Sure.

538
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,510
怎么了
What?

539
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:00,880
现在不行
Not now.

540
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:02,340
好吧
Okay.

541
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:04,030
我得走了
I should go.

542
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:07,310
-我只是  我以为  -我知道
- I just... it seemed... - I know.

543
00:26:09,560 --> 00:26:11,210
我们不能再这样了
We can't start this again.

544
00:26:11,210 --> 00:26:13,170
我结束掉的事不会再做
When I end something, I end it.

545
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:16,900
那你大老远的把我从纽约叫来干什么
So why'd you have me come all the way down from New York?

546
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:20,180
我错了
It was a mistake.

547
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:23,380
对不起  亚当
I'm sorry, Adam.

548
00:26:23,380 --> 00:26:25,530
我不应该掺杂私情的
I should've kept it business.

549
00:26:27,290 --> 00:26:29,140
我最不喜欢的就是你这点
Side of you I like the least.

550
00:26:41,330 --> 00:26:43,810
没有错可言  克莱尔
There are no mistakes, Claire.

551
00:27:00,540 --> 00:27:01,790
晚上好
Hello.

552
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,960
再来点酒
More wine?

553
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,530
