How was your day?

554
00:27:11,850 --> 00:27:14,200
-很好  -亚当也好吗
- Good. - Adam well?

555
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,600
是的
He is.

556
00:27:16,610 --> 00:27:18,060
我们刚吃过晚饭
We just had dinner.

557
00:27:22,330 --> 00:27:24,370
