I appreciate that this was not easy.

561
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:38,120
难才对我们胃口  不是吗
Well, we don't like easy, do we?

562
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:40,490
事实证明  确实如此
Oh, the evidence would suggest it.

563
